{"tid":2002413,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插攪拌機求指教]遣散費一問","createTime":"2020-05-05T07:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T16:44:48.000Z","uid":17359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c97b0864c0b436243f3f92713b67146a357eba56","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟係3月30日被炒<br />\n即時出埋糧同補左一個月代通知金比我<br />\n<br />\n遣散費就話要等3-5個星期<br />\n4月29號左右check左mpf<br />\n已經扣左僱主果5%<br />\n<br />\n但到而家仲未收到張cheque<br />\n<br />\n想請教一下呢個情況是咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14756f678f56f0dad6760ed621193e08622323b","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de79969b4bd6348117ae7814c070ab3ef4c03152","tid":2002413,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57l_whole.htm#Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57l_whole.htm%23Q4&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=7b3b750b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57l_whole.htm#Q4</a><br />\n<br />\n如 僱 主 因 裁 員 而 解 僱 僱 員 ， 應 盡 快 向 僱 員 支 付 遣 散 費 。 而 《僱 傭 條 例》 亦 規 定 ， 僱 主 必 須 在 收 到 僱 員 以 書 面 發 出 申 索 遣 散 費 的 通 知 後 的 2 個 月 內 ， 向 僱 員 支 付 遣 散 費 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係你要追鳩個僱主，我上年被遣散一個月代通知金尾糧和遣散費，一炮過比我。以防萬一，被無良僱主拖，我建議去你返工個區的勞工處問。"},{"pid":"9d852439920fcdeb6c5b6e665fd5770b55ce453c","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de79969b4bd6348117ae7814c070ab3ef4c03152","tid":2002413,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"