<br />\n話要等3-5星期<br />\n<br />\n問舊公司個hr又話控制唔到<br />\n屌佢老母3月30號到而家過撚哂5個星期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e833d19a5c015c04ceb8ed137583bf47a0284b","tid":2002413,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6b9235b28c6a1047164b37ea6a93093ee2d4b44","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d4f81e88bdc3c3628fd3e97552efdc962faa90","tid":2002413,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"正常係7日內要出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"Mpf係Manulife搞<br />\n話要等3-5星期<br />\n<br />\n問舊公司個hr又話控制唔到<br />\n屌佢老母3月30號到而家過撚哂5個星期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/main/employee/offsetting_of_long_service_payment_and_severance.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Ftch%2Fmain%2Femployee%2Foffsetting_of_long_service_payment_and_severance.jsp&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=885dc5cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfa.org.hk/tch/main/employee/offsetting_of_long_service_payment_and_severance.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵銷程序<br />\n進行抵銷的方法有兩種，視乎僱主有否先向你支付長期服務金／遣散費而定。<br />\n<br />\n僱主已向你支付長期服務金／遣散費：如僱主已向你支付全數長期服務金／遣散費，僱主可以透過受託人安排，從你的帳戶內提取由僱主供款所產生的累算權益。僱主可能需要你書面確認已收妥該筆款項，以便向受託人申請抵銷款項。<br />\n<br />\n僱主未向你支付長期服務金／遣散費：如僱主仍未向你支付任何部分的長期服務金／遣散費，你可以直接向受託人提交書面申請，以提取帳戶內僱主供款所產生的累算權益。受託人將要求你提供證據，以證明你有權獲發長期服務金／遣散費，而僱主並未向你發放該筆款項。<br />\n<br />\n提示：如僱主沒有向你支付長期服務金／遣散費，你應該要求僱主向你發出一封函件，證明僱主尚未向你支付你有權獲得的長期服務金／遣散費，在函件上最好附有僱主的授權簽署及公司印章。當受託人為你提取累算權益作為長期服務金／遣散費時，該封函件將是有用的文件。"},{"pid":"a0bf8ef0c0854129fb5a7df3007c199ab013a617","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"有齊證明我可以拎長期服務金 <br />\n決定等埋呢個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n冇就去勞記開file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e2b6aac88ed74f7a976dd9a569f29be24592b3","tid":2002413,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0bf8ef0c0854129fb5a7df3007c199ab013a617","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"有齊證明我可以拎長期服務金 <br />\n決定等埋呢個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n冇就去勞記開file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"做左幾耐？"},{"pid":"3790cf1645cd81f99cf92d454a7468dacde8161a","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19e2b6aac88ed74f7a976dd9a569f29be24592b3","tid":2002413,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0bf8ef0c0854129fb5a7df3007c199ab013a617","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"有齊證明我可以拎長期服務金 <br />\n決定等埋呢個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n冇就去勞記開file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"做左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"16年6月開始做"},{"pid":"a5c82c421f79b8204f35a009dda060bc5680c13f","tid":2002413,"uid":3744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3790cf1645cd81f99cf92d454a7468dacde8161a","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19e2b6aac88ed74f7a976dd9a569f29be24592b3","tid":2002413,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0bf8ef0c0854129fb5a7df3007c199ab013a617","tid":2002413,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"有齊證明我可以拎長期服務金 <br />\n決定等埋呢個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n冇就去勞記開file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"做左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"16年6月開始做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"長期服務金唔係要做夠5年先有咩"},{"pid":"47186a24b7f2a44